pting similar themes, aim to represent "lazy and unemployed" youth and Gen-Z, offering an alternative to established political factions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-gets-its-own-cockroach-awaam-party-as-indias-viral-cjp-sparks-cross-border-satire-wave/articleshow/131263286.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-gets-its-own-cockroach-awaam-party-as-indias-viral-cjp-sparks-cross-border-satire-wave/articleshow/131263286.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T17:37:54+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131263333,imgsize-1128827.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘It would be a big mistake’: WHO Africa chief warns against underestimating Ebola virus risk in Congo, Uganda]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131264292.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[WHO's Africa director warns against underestimating the Ebola outbreak in DRC and Uganda, stressing that even one case could spread widely due to the lack of a vaccine for this strain. He urged for greater international attention, highlighting the potential risk to all from a single infected individual. Efforts are underway to boost testing and community engagement amidst challenges.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/it-would-be-a-big-mistake-who-africa-chief-warns-against-underestimating-ebola-virus-risk-in-congo-uganda/articleshow/131264292.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/it-would-be-a-big-mistake-who-africa-chief-warns-against-underestimating-ebola-virus-risk-in-congo-uganda/articleshow/131264292.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T18:52:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://